Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:04.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:11.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:23.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:28.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:34.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:39.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:44.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:02.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:07.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:13.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:17.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:04.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:11.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:23.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:28.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:34.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:39.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:44.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:56.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:02.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:07.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:13.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:17.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:16.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:22.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:52.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:56.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:03.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:07.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:13.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:18.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:24.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:37.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:16.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:22.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:52.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:56.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:03.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:07.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:13.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:18.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:24.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:37.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的點心也好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果葉太郎和依子也來一起吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他們倆差不多也該回來了..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐她..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真緒醬的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快點把大小姐帶過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想綁架真緒醬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綁架？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺們啊 是大小姐的父親派來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們在害怕什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉它不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准欺負白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准欺負愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不是不可以 只要你肯乖乖過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真..真緒醬不能..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很弱還這麼纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要送真緒去外國？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是總帥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 真緒的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人真的很善良..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於刻意保持距離的我們也非常關心..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這樣的真緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想至少把這寶貴之物交給她..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把真緒大人帶走的人是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所有人..都是被父親所救的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被父親所救？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從小被一個叫「幫」的犯罪組織培養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並在那裏被迫做出傷天害理的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父親把我們從那裏救了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是多虧了父親我才能夠來這裏工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我所毀滅的 名為「幫」的組織的殘黨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花小姐的父親 難不成是金剛寺先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你.你也是騎士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎的事 真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是想要為父親幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒想到他會強行把真緒大人帶走..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放開我 依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去吧 依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要把真緒醬..把真緒醬..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲已經很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都沒有錯 愛麗絲和我都已經盡全力了..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以..已經..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎大人是不會說這種話的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「沒辦法」什麼的..這種話..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡的葉太郎大人是不會..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}致Knightlancer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？金剛寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據報告稱 出現了可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是何許人也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說騎著一匹白馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往後就要去國外生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這次你的內心足夠堅強的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就儘管去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨你如果想妨礙的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 凱太寵孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長..長槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成 你也是騎士麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一位女僕 所以這只是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處罰而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫助我 給我帶來勇氣 帶來希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次遇到了真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成為KnightLancer那樣的真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和KnightLancer不同 葉太郎很沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當初我想幫助因為餓肚子而煩惱的葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer也會這麼做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了葉太郎之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲和白姬 還有依子也都跑來陪伴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常地開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這一切都是KnightLancer的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很膽小 一直只會逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便明白真緒大人的處境 我還是什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我一直對她視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我明明鄭重發誓再也不和犯罪扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我也沒能扔掉這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎先生 我來指引你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金剛寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓開 金剛寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須趕到真緒的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒的願望 真緒的感受 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望真緒能夠一直擁有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金剛寺先生也能感受到真緒真正的心願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回答我 金剛寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用行動傳達你的意願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麓王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麓王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎 不 KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你執意要與我作對的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以騎士之禮儀 我只有全力迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親 被稱為傳說之騎士的男人趕赴戰場之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定會帶上一口棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺入其中的不是敵人 就是自己..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒之槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼意思？森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先鋒之槍應該只有你能..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手持先鋒之槍的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用全力來與你對決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長槍突擊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把靈魂獻給公主之時 騎士..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將成為至高的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向您發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士絕不會背叛善良女士的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在何時 無論您身處何處 我將畢生守護您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？起來啊 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人..老大不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 快起來啊爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕快起來的話 俺又要做壞事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做不該做的事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想讓你爸爸死掉的話 就馬上從那讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了呢 鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎..得到了先鋒之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來只有唯一的受選騎士才能使用先鋒之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而它的擁有者本應是森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 先鋒之槍卻對葉太郎產生了反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子 葉太郎身上到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐 父親他..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士和公主現在相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動真緒 如果你真的對她的命運著想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就絕對不要接近她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把她永遠深鎖於高塔之中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士為了保護公主而賭上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主在騎士的守護下綻放光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是那兩個孩子的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把你對於沒能保護好結真的悔恨強加給真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒是我和結真的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點你別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:20:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而葉太郎 那孩子是騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當秘而不發的力量覺醒之時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎就會成為真正的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定會把公主守護到底的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合你哦 真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到真緒穿這種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒不是想成為英雄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放棄成為英雄的念頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？真緒醬之前明明那麼想成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明說過自己想變得跟KnightLancer一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後 我要成為配得上KnightLancer的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer一直把我稱呼為女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須成為不辱此名的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話就會讓KnightLancer蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要成為配得上KnightLancer的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 成為KnightLancer的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 被KnightLancer求婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer發誓要畢生守護我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定就是要和我一生相伴的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不是那個意思..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士絕對不能空言虛語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依..依子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊 葉太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和真緒醬結婚什麼的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能說這種話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬才6歲而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可您卻..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成..葉太郎大人真的是蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要娶我為妻的是KnightLancer哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是因為..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}讓您久等了、女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 番長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了 白姬番長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬是番長？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬 用恐怖統治著學園 高高在上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是超乎想像的壞小孩嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬..住手..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬的蹄癢了
